# Publish-exclude discipline for the Composer dist package.
#
# Packagist/Composer serve the "dist" tarball produced by `git archive`
# (equivalently `composer archive`), which honours `export-ignore`. Everything
# marked here is porting-process audit machinery that must NOT ship inside the
# published `signalwire/sdk` package — only the library (src/), the bin entry
# point, and the landing-page/manifest files should.
#
# Verify authoritatively with the artifact_deny gate's --listing mode:
#   git archive --format=tar HEAD | tar -t \
#     | python3 ../porting-sdk/scripts/artifact_deny.py --port php --listing -

# --- porting-audit contract files (root) ---
CHECKLIST.md            export-ignore
DOC_AUDIT_IGNORE.md     export-ignore
PROGRESS.md             export-ignore
REST_COVERAGE_GAPS.md   export-ignore
PORT_ADDITIONS.md       export-ignore
PORT_OMISSIONS.md       export-ignore
PORT_SIGNATURE_OMISSIONS.md export-ignore
PORT_TEST_OMISSIONS.md  export-ignore
PORT_EXAMPLE_OMISSIONS.md export-ignore

# --- generated audit oracles / coverage data ---
port_signatures.json    export-ignore
port_surface.json       export-ignore
audit_coverage.json     export-ignore
audit_coverage_baseline.json export-ignore

# --- audit harness examples + emit tools (not library code) ---
examples/RelayAuditHarness.php  export-ignore
examples/RestAuditHarness.php   export-ignore
examples/SkillsAuditHarness.php export-ignore
scripts/emit_corpus.php export-ignore
scripts/emit_skills.php export-ignore

# --- allowlists + porting-process docs/dirs (not library code) ---
ROOT_HYGIENE_ALLOW.md   export-ignore
ARTIFACT_DENY_ALLOW.md  export-ignore
META_CONSISTENT_ALLOW.md export-ignore
.gitattributes          export-ignore
scripts/                export-ignore
tests/                  export-ignore
